import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";

function TextControlsExample() {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
        <Form.Label style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}>reportId</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="text" style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}/>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
        <Form.Label style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}>doctorId</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="text" style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}/>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
        <Form.Label style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}>patientId</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="text" style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}/>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
        <Form.Label style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}>reportOne</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={5} style={{fontFamily:"sans-serif"}}/>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
        <Form.Label>reportTwo</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={5} />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
        <Form.Label>prescription</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={5} />
      </Form.Group>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default TextControlsExample;
